{"word":"G3741 - ὅσιος - hósios - hos'-ee-os - Holy","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὅσιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hósios"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hos'-ee-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Holy"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பரிசுத்தமான, கிருபையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"undefiled by sin, free from wickedness, religiously observing every moral obligation, pure, holy, pious"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Of uncertain affinity; properly <i>right</i> (by intrinsic or divine character; thus distinguished from <a href=\"#/G1342 - δίκαιος - díkaios - dik'-ah-yos/1342\">G1342</a>, which refers rather to <i>human</i> statutes and relations; from <a href=\"#/G2413 - ἱερός - hierós - hee-er-os'/2413\">G2413</a>, which denotes formal <i>consecration</i>; and from <a href=\"#/G40 - ἅγιος - hágios - hag'-ee-os/40\">G40</a>, which relates to <i>purity</i> from defilement), that is, <i>hallowed</i> (<i>pious</i>, <i>sacred</i>, <i>sure</i>): - holy, mercy, shalt be."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3741 - ὅσιος - hósios - hos'-ee-os/3741\">G3741</a>, <a href=\"#/G3742 - ὁσιότης - hosiótēs - hos-ee-ot'-ace/3742\">G3742</a>, <a href=\"#/G3743 - ὁσίως - hosíōs - hos-ee-oce'/3743\">G3743</a>, <a href=\"#/G462 - ἀνόσιος - anósios - an-os'-ee-os/462\">G462</a>"}]}